<h2>Books</h2>
<ul>
<li>Wickham, H., &amp; Grolemund, G. (2017). R for Data Science. O’Reilly Media. <a href="http://r4ds.had.co.nz"><i class="fa-solid fa-link" aria-label="link"></i></a></li>
