<li>Lewis-Beck, M. (1980). Applied Regression: An Introduction. Volume 22 of Quantitative Applications in the Social Sciences. Sage Publications. <a href="http://a.co/2zyfhXj"><i class="fa-solid fa-link" aria-label="link"></i></a></li>
<li>Berry, W., &amp; Feldman, S. (1985). Multiple Regression in Practice. Issue 50. Quantitative Applications in the Social Sciences. Sage Publications. <a href="http://a.co/8jcU0ef"><i class="fa-solid fa-link" aria-label="link"></i></a></li>
